- [ ] **[SVG 1.0 Specification (2001)](https://www.w3.org/TR/2001/PR-SVG-20010719/intro.html)** - Original SVG proposal showing introduction structure, design principles, and rationale for SVG as a standard. Essential for understanding how to position FBF.SVG within the SVG family.

